            "title": "A股低收逾1%　一周累計報跌扭轉升勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市低收逾1%至逾2%，一周計滬深俱跌，扭轉連升兩周走勢，深股累跌2.7%。兩市合計成交15508.56億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人形機器人、汽車產業鏈股份下跌，中藥、航運、海工裝備概念股造好。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數失守3400點水平，收報3364點，跌44點或1.29%，創逾1星期低位，今早開報3401點，跌7點或0.21%，上午見3414點，升6點或0.18%，為全日高位，下午跌破上午低位，最低見3355點，跌53點或1.56%，為全日低位。成交6231.64億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成份指數收報10687點，跌191點，跌幅1.76%。今早開報19843，跌36點或0.33%，最高見10843，跌36點或0.33%，隨即拾級而下，至下午2時後低見10656，挫223點或2.05%，成交9276.92億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300收報3914，跌60點或1.52%，創業板指數報2152點，跌47點，跌幅2.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，滬股累計跌1.6%，深證成指跌2.7%，創業板指數跌3.3%，全部扭轉前1星期升勢。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">機器人股集體調整，夏廈精密(001306.SZ)、信質集團(002664.SZ)跌停。股份跌多漲少，滬深兩市共逾4000隻股份下調。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海洋經濟概念爆發，海默科技(300084.SZ)升 20.03%，報9.59元 ; 神開股份(002278)10.04%，報11.9元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14793798-a%e8%82%a1%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be1%e3%80%80%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e5%a0%b1%e8%b7%8c%e6%89%ad%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87%e5%8b%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-21 15:55:44",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
